Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.89,0:00:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因哈特同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早啊  爱因哈特同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊  薇薇欧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.07,0:00:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中等科的一年级生  爱因哈特·斯崔特斯同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.87,0:00:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因哈特同学是个很历害的格斗技练习者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新生贝鲁卡式的古流武术  霸王流的传人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是贝鲁卡诸王时代的君王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.73,0:00:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霸王英格瓦尔特的正统后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又强又漂亮  我还完全比不上她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.14,0:00:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是想和她尽量亲近些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起训练  一起聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.88,0:01:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇欧同学  你的教学楼是那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  爱因哈特同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.43,0:01:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意不要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我会注意的
Comment: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:03:01.10,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)\pos(347,620)\be2}「崭新的心」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是考试啊  真是要命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一学期的期中考试  必须要努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是考试一结束  算上周末就是一个四天的考试假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  会有一个精彩的旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说住宿和娱乐的准备都已经到位了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那我们可不能败给区区考试啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了大家能一起旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标  100分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃里奥  琦萝  你们那边怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  刚才已经顺利完成交接了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和计划一样  周末开始就能休假了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就能按计划和大家一起去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:03:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天的大自然之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及  露提希亚也会加入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪大家一起离岗训练
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有诺威和昴不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吵了  我们又不是去玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴是去离岗训练的  而我要负责带那群小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说归说  你从网上买的泳衣还有河边玩的器具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当姐姐我不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然乱拆人家的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发货信息上都写的很清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么不好  诺威兼职和救助队的实习都很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好  真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了不是去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因哈特也一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:05:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这样想的  不过现在才要去约她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说集训？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我还要训练
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说嘛  就是过去训练的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我和老姐在  薇薇欧也会去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习对手不会缺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还能看到魔导士等级AA和S+的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便还有个熟悉历史  并且拥有你们国家稀有传记的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有四天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就当被诳了一回  过来看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是觉得没劲  你就去闷头跑步或者独自练习也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.51,0:05:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对会是一次有意义的体验
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我会发邮件告诉你详情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先加油解决今天的考试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此这般  考试阶段也顺利结束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试结束  你们都辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家考得怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到花丸评价了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们三个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是优等生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来就能光明正大地出门玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Good job
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(712,646)\fs36}Raising Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  拂晓之心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那莉奥和珂罗娜必须先回家一趟进行准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因哈特同学  还有诺威
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听诺威小姐说了训练集训的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:07:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我可以一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  我全力欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇欧  快请她们进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因哈特同学  请进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不告诉她同行的事是做对了呢  诺威
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  效果比预计还好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面  爱因哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是薇薇欧的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小女一直以来承蒙关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你很擅长格斗技对吧  好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈你等一下  爱因哈特同学很文静的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  弄得那么吵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来出行的人员就都齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,途中顺道去两位的家  然后就直接出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了薇薇欧  换洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦  克莉丝  过来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  昴小姐她们和我们分开行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和昴还有迪亚娜她们约好在次元港的检票口碰头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多工作也该弄完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待集训啊  还有久违的模拟战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是很期待  但又不能在薇薇欧和爱因哈特她们面前出丑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的  出发前能做完的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Let's work hard
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们加油干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.39,0:09:12.43,POS2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,605)\bord1.5}无人世界加尔纳吉  阿尔皮诺家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人数就定下了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  又要劳烦您照顾了  梅格奴女士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  那我等着你们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说牙龙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的才能连自己都有点害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟这次的接待是史无前例的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多层建筑构成的演习场用作陆战魔导士演习
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和牙龙亲手制作的训练场地用作大家的体能训练
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建在我家边上住宿屋内装外装全部升级
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:10:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖出来的天然温泉也被我倾力改造成治愈空间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇欧还有其他人  我等你们来我家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露提希亚  来帮我尝尝汤的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因哈特同学  这四天就请多多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  要是有切磋的机会就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我才是要请你赐教
Comment: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从首都格拉纳加乘临港次元船到加尔纳吉需要约四小时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终年气候温暖  自然资源丰富
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友  露·露也住在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二位好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有劳关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们能来我太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃的也准备了很多  你们随意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露·露  好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  薇薇欧  珂罗娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和莉奥还是第一次直接见面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前都是通过屏幕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  比屏幕上看着还可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露·露  这位就是邮件里提过的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是爱因哈特·斯崔特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是露提希亚·阿尔皮诺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在这里  也是薇薇欧的朋友  14岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露对历史之类很熟悉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？埃里奥和琦萝还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  他们俩现在在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:11:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃里奥  琦萝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃里奥又长高了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也稍微长高了一点哦  1.5厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因哈特  给你介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两位都是我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是埃里奥·蒙蒂阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是琦萝·鲁·露西和飞龙弗利德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有个小不点  不过我们三个人是同岁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  人家明明长高了1.5厘米呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是爱因哈特·斯崔特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  请多关照  爱因哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因哈特同学  抱歉抱歉  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的召唤兽  也是重要的家人  叫牙龙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失…失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一开始也被吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  吃饭之前大人们要进行训练吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们要去哪里玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是先去河边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐也来呗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因哈特也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大家换好衣服在训练场集合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这边也换上泳装  在屋后集合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳装？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉奥耍赖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因哈特同学也过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  叫你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺威小姐  可以的话我想去训练…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  就当是准备运动  去玩一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  那些小家伙们玩水的方法可是高难度的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因哈特同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也可以一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  「因为外装是布偶  弄湿了的话就飞不起来了」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也挺不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  往对岸游个来回
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家来比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.71,0:14:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  注意到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:14:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说是精力旺盛么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说…旺盛过头的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  没什么在水里活动的经验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来对自己的体力还是有些自信的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我觉得你已经很了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在水中使出爆发力需要用到不同的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那薇薇欧她们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概每周两次的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在游泳池一边玩一边训练
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然而然的就拥有了柔软而且有耐力的肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.57,0:15:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  还算是比较有趣的体验吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能够帮到你的话就更好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  机会难得  给你看些有趣的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇欧  莉奥  珂罗娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给爱因哈特看看「水斩」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水斩？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点小把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便还能检查一下打击能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.01,0:16:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因哈特的格斗技也很强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要来试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水中无法施展大幅度的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要利用阻力比较小的回旋力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能柔软地…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天然淋浴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打出了5米左右的水柱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的话  初速度太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.65,0:17:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始要放松
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢地向着打出的方向  突然加速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之中迅速地注入力量的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起势要放松
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,途中要慢慢的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只在冲击的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力出击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比刚才稍微远了一些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以再继续练一会儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.89,0:18:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽情地来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.54,0:18:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因哈特玩得开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇欧她们和她在一起  肯定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有诺威师傅跟着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息时间延长一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:19:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才没觉得累呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.38,0:19:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  开饭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家集合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让大家着凉  我准备了很多热乎乎的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会烤很多的  大家也要使劲吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家玩的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  薇薇欧和爱因哈特没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人一直在练习水斩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.69,0:19:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  好好吃呢这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶嘿  这是我引以为傲的调味汁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇欧同学  你们一直是这样接受诺威小姐的教导么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  并不总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一开始只是和昴小姐学习一些格斗的基础
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来在我努力自学的时候  诺威向我搭了话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后  她就抽时间教我许多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后不知不觉的就连珂罗娜和莉奥也一起教了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很温柔的  诺威她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点羡慕你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我一直是独自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过从此以后  你就不再是一个人了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.07,0:21:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过流派之类的  还是要分开的对吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.74,0:21:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那个  没关系  我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古流武术和近代格斗技  无法走到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要是偶尔能像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:21:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是片刻的结伴而行
